<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-04-30T04:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-04-30T04:00:00-05:00" n="34" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d34">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 European War 1939/10470:
                                Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Steinhardt</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-04-30T12:00:00+03:00">April
                                        30, 1941—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received April 30—11:20
                                    a.m.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>880. <hi rend="italic">Pravda</hi> today published the following
                                despatch from its Tallinn correspondent: <quote rend="blockquote">
                                    <p>“According to trustworthy information received here on April
                                        26th, four German transports arrived in the Finnish port of
                                        Abo (Turku) from which were disembarked approximately 12,000
                                        German troops equipped with arms, tanks, artillery, etc. On
                                        April 28th these troops began to leave for Tampere.”<note n="68" xml:id="d34fn68">Tammerfors.</note>
                                    </p>
                                </quote>
                            </p>
                            <p>Repeated to Helsinki.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Steinhardt</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>